race.description: Become A Brc Member Maiden Plate
race.comment: CHERRY BOMSHELL (12) has the race fitness/experience. Just missed in a Randwick trial and then contested a $500,000 Magic Millions 2YO Plate on debut and didn't have the best of it at a $13 quote. Maps well and Ben Thompson is booked today. She sets a decent standard for the newcomers. SWEET REBELLION (10) debuts and owns a 7.2L Gold Coast trial win. Has a 3kg claim and is sure to make her presence felt. HIGH AUTHORITY (11) debuts and just missed in a recent Doomben trial. Has the outside gate but he can get into the money. SLING (2) debuts and will get every chance from an inside barrier. Is likely better than the trial finish suggests.
